<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.2">
<l>īca ṉavaṉallā tillai yeṉaniṉaintu</l>
<l>kūci maṉattakattuk koṇṭiruntu - pēci</l>
<l>maṟavātu vāḻvārai maṇṇulakat teṉṟum</l>
<l>piṟavāmaik kākkum pirāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who live on the earth world without forgetting,</l>
<l>thinking there is no lord but him,</l>
<l>keeping [it] humbly in mind [and] speaking [so]</l>
<l>always the lord with protect from being born [again].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
